          Discussions will take place on the <a href="http://mail.openjdk.java.net/mailman/listinfo/adoption-discuss">Mailing List</a>, or via
          the <a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-build/issues">Github issues</a>; and consensus recorded on this project website or the
          appropriate GitHub repo wiki as appropriate:

          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-build" target="_blank">openjdk-build</a> - Build scripts and other infrastructure to create binaries</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-website" target="_blank">openjdk-website</a> - This website</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-website-backend" target="_blank">openjdk-website-backend</a> - Scripts to integrate GitHub with this website</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-releases" target="_blank">openjdk-releases</a> - OpenJDK tagged releases</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-nightly" target="_blank">openjdk-nightly</a> - Nightly releases</li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-jdk8u" target="_blank">openjdk-jdk8u</a> - A clone of the OpenJDK jdk8u forest</li>
          </ul>
        </p>

